@page
@model PrivacyModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<div class="privacy-policy">
    <p class="lead">Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how ChatApp collects, uses, and protects your information when you use our application.</p>
    
    <p>By using ChatApp, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.</p>

    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We collect the following types of information to provide and improve our service:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> When you register for an account, we ask for personal information such as your username, email address, and a password. Your password is encrypted and we cannot see it.</li>
        <li><strong>Message Content:</strong> We collect the messages you send and receive through the application in order to deliver them to the correct users.</li>
        <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> We may automatically collect basic information when you use our service, such as your IP address and connection times. This helps us maintain security and troubleshoot problems.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>We use the information we collect for the following purposes:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>To create and manage your account</li>
        <li>To provide the core real-time messaging service</li>
        <li>To identify you and secure your account</li>
        <li>To monitor and improve the performance and security of our application</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>We will not sell your personal information to third parties.</strong></p>

    <h2>3. Data Security</h2>
    <p>We take reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access or disclosure. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure, so we cannot guarantee its absolute security.</p>

    <h2>4. Your Choices</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> You can review and update your account information through your login settings.</li>
        <li><strong>Account Deletion:</strong> You can delete your account at any time. When you delete your account, your personal information will be removed from our active databases.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>5. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.</p>

    <h2>6. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at: 
        <a href="mailto:privacy@chatapp.com">privacy@chatapp.com</a>
    </p>
</div>
